stories.title: Start me up
stories.subTitle: India's opening combinations
stories.summary: The time is ripe to groom another opener for India in one day internationals

stories.title: India dominate England comprehensively
stories.summary:
For a nation that heaps expectations on its cricketers, India's
dominance over England at Colombo was hugely satisfying, to
say the least

stories.title: Sehwag's temperament is exemplary
stories.summary:
Is there still any doubt that the Indian batting line-up is the
most explosive, the most attractive in world cricket today
